Blessed be. 

As October comes to a close, I've decided to close this site too. I'm moving out. Where to? Only <a href="http://ohoneohoneoneoh.livejournal.com/friends">friends</a> would <a href="http://ohoneohoneoneoh.livejournal.com/13223.html">know</a>.

This journal will be purged soon.
